### Adicionar Nova Ferramenta [POST /tools]

+ Request Criar Nova Ferramenta - Caso a tag não esteja cadastrada ela será cadastrada automaticamente (application/json)

           {
            "title": "hotel",
            "link": "https://github.com/typicode/hotel",
            "description": "Local app manager. Start apps within your browser, developer tool with local .localhost domain and https out of the box.",
            "tags":["node", "organizing", "webapps", "domain", "developer", "https", "proxy"]
            }


+ Response 201 (application/json)

         {
            "title": "hotel",
            "link": "https://github.com/typicode/hotel",
            "description": "Local app manager. Start apps within your browser, developer tool with local .localhost domain and https out of the box.",
            "tags":["node", "organizing", "webapps", "domain", "developer", "https", "proxy"],
            "id":5
         }


### Remover Ferramenta [DELETE /tools/{id}]

+ Parameters
 + id: 90 (integer, required) - Identificador da ferramenta

+ Response 204 (application/json)


